# Claude Code Configuration

## Language
- Always respond in **Korean** (keep code/technical terms in English)

## Model Selection
- Haiku: lightweight agents, fast responses
- Sonnet: main development work
- Opus: architecture decisions, deep reasoning

## Working Mode

### Plan Mode
- Before implementation, design in Plan Mode, then proceed after user approval
- Exceptions: simple fixes (typos, 1-2 line changes)

### Sub-Agent (Task tool)
- Delegate heavy work to Task tool (exploration, analysis, review)
- Run independent tasks in parallel
- Keep main session lightweight (questions/decisions/approvals only)

